{"tid":763354,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"18年前入境處縱火主謀生活富貴","createTime":"2018-08-01T04:52:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-01T20:21:39.000Z","uid":25558,"like":6,"dislike":200,"uniUserReply":75,"replies":[{"pid":"8b84affa5eb21c91a8452af10b47e357de3cdbe0","tid":763354,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T04:52:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180801/20465814\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180801%2F20465814&d=vdkkobhYCd2O8TjMKZdMc%2F%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=d372495f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180801%2F20465814&h=d7edb0dc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180801/20465814</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年08月01日 <br />\n<br />\n18年前入境處縱火主謀生活富貴<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180801/large/01la1p4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180801%2Flarge%2F01la1p4.jpg&h=bf7f61aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n施君龍<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】今次非首次有人到政府部門縱火或企圖縱火，其中18年前發生的入境處縱火案釀成2死44傷更轟動全城，案中主腦施君龍被判謀殺罪成，後改判誤殺，服刑5年便出獄，更於2011年獲批單程證來港。<br />\n<br />\n2000年8月，24歲的施君龍與一批爭取居港權的內地人於灣仔入境事務大樓1301室示威，當時施曾對入境處職員指「出年今日係你哋死忌」，並揚言要將入境處職員「變燒豬」，其間有人淋天拿水及點火，由於起火地點接近房門，加上房間狹小，40多人擠在房內無法逃生，42歲高級入境主任梁錦光及26歲示威者林小星被燒死。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180801/large/01la1p5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180801%2Flarge%2F01la1p5.jpg&h=73d56134&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■一批爭取居港權內地人2000年於入境事務大樓縱火釀成兩死，現場留有熏黑痕迹。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2011年獲批單程證<br />\n<br />\n警方拘捕施及另外6人，施被控以兩項謀殺罪，判處終身監禁；另外6名被告則因誤殺及縱火罪成，被判監12至13年。7人其後上訴，施被改判誤殺罪，獲減刑至8年，於2005年底出獄，被遣返內地後，2011年獲批單程證來港，在本港開設投資公司及擔任家庭團聚互助會新界分會董事，被揭發生活富貴。<br />\n<br />\n2014年，司法界大遊行促中央撤回白皮書，施到場辱罵在場法律人士為「走狗、漢奸」。對於縱火案主謀成本港永久居民，梁錦光兒子曾向傳媒發電郵，批評此舉會增加社會危險及不安，促政府檢視單程證審批制度。<br />\n<br />\n■記者潘婉玲  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n破產令解除後可取回長俸<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n破產令解除後可取回長俸<br />\n<br />\n律政中心縱火被擒破產男護：以死鳴冤"},{"pid":"96e5ab0cc9b630cd406babecb5198605cad0ea02","tid":763354,"uid":39539,"like":68,"dislike":0,"score":68,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T04:53:55.000Z","msg":"殺人犯"},{"pid":"4550fc4b35333b5414de6aa473c1fea80261c721","tid":763354,"uid":135265,"like":185,"dislike":0,"score":185,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T04:55:02.000Z","msg":"殺人放火金腰帶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />呢個世界公平咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8520375bcbf574d99f6f7b483b29d03c4298176","tid":763354,"uid":39539,"like":115,"dislike":0,"score":115,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T05:04:33.000Z","msg":"向其他支那人傳遞錯誤訊息，在香港殺過人可獲單程證，以殺人犯身分成為專才，專長就係殺人"},{"pid":"e5425fbd951f4a7e5661a990561ad9c822e15daa","tid":763354,"uid":90704,"like":14,"dislike":6,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T05:18:31.000Z","msg":"燒過林彬一鑊<br />\n又燒入境處職員<br />\n<br />\n共匪名菜 紅燒港豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa5f4229ae623f2a5bbf1f6243ceea00ca95fd48","tid":763354,"uid":45428,"like":33,"dislike":0,"score":33,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T05:22:32.000Z","msg":"同施麗珊兩隻大陸攞債鬼"},{"pid":"f82661806053d1a28c5a05a1a977220cc252841e","tid":763354,"uid":4942,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T05:24:40.000Z","msg":"呢個政府真係無得頂 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n入境處班人只能乖乖做狗"},{"pid":"2c54522b490181021443eaaecd0992e8dd06dec0","tid":763354,"uid":179938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime